# Grace CLI Configuration
#
# Grace itself does not read environment variables — runtime config lives in
# .grace/config.yaml (see `grace config show`). This file documents only the
# one optional env var that the Claude Code CLI (which Grace shells out to)
# consults during authentication.

# Optional Claude Code CLI auth fallback. Only needed if `claude setup-token`
# fails on your installed Claude Code version. Requires API credit at
# console.anthropic.com.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_api_key_here
